        {
            "block_label": "figure_title",
            "block_content": "<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Figure 5. Comparing INT3-g128 quantized Vicuna models with FP16 counterparts under GPT-4 evaluation protocol (Chiang et al., 2023). More winning cases (in blue) indicate better performance. AWQ consistently improves the quantized performance compared to RTN and GPTQ (Frantar et al., 2022), showing generalization to instruction-tuned models.</div>\n",
            "block_bbox": [
